settings.settingsLabel: Modify settings for the documentation site, including visuals, accessibility, and general configurations.
settings.refreshNote1: Note: This setting WILL refresh the page.
settings.refreshNote2: Note: This setting requires a page refresh.
settings.devBranchLabel: Enable this switch to display updates from both stable and latest development versions, instead of just stable ones.
settings.hideLoadingLabel: Enable this switch to stop seeing the loading screen when loading the website.
settings.hideSidebarTooltipsLabel: Enable to hide the tooltips from the sidebar/menu when you hover (PC) or click/hold (Mobile) a function.
settings.disableFoldersLabel: Enable if you don't want functions, events, and enums to be displayed in folders if the package allows them.
settings.lowSaturationLabel: Enable this switch to activate low saturation mode, desaturating the entire website.
